12 Sec. 1. 8 V.S.A. ยง 4212 is added to read:
13 ยง 4212. MINIMUM REIMBURSEMENT RATES FOR LABOR
14 (a) The Commissioner of Financial Regulation shall conduct a market
15 survey of the hourly labor rates charged by automobile repair facilities in
16 Vermont. In addition, the Commissioner shall investigate the labor rates paid
17 by automobile insurance companies for repair work in Vermont. The
18 Commissioner shall compare these rates with the average rates in other New
19 England states and may review any additional data the Commissioner deems
20 relevant to such rates, such as national data.
